<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset - AuthKit</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            color: #4a90e2;
        }
        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">Password Reset Request</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your password for your AuthKit account. Click the button below to reset your password. This link will expire in one hour.</p>
            <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you have any concerns.</p>
            <a href="{{url}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
            <p>If the button above doesnâ€™t work, copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
            <p><a href="{{url}}">{{url}}</a></p>
            <p>Thank you,<br>The AuthKit Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Please do not reply to this email. For support, contact <a href="mailto:support@authkit.com">support@authkit.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
